---
import { Icon } from "astro-icon/components";
---

<div class="w-full max-w-4xl mx-auto space-y-12">
    <section
        class="bg-white dark:bg-slate-900 rounded-3xl p-8 shadow-sm border border-slate-100 dark:border-slate-800"
    >
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-black text-slate-800 dark:text-white mb-6 flex items-center gap-3">
            <div
                class="p-3 bg-indigo-100 dark:bg-indigo-900/30 rounded-2xl text-indigo-600 dark:text-indigo-400"
            >
                <Icon name="mdi:brain" class="w-8 h-8" />
            </div>
            ¿Cómo funciona este Test?
        </h2>
        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 items-center">
            <div class="prose dark:prose-invert text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-300">
                <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed">
                    Esta herramienta mide tu <strong>tiempo de reacción visual</strong> con precisión
                    quirúrgica. Calculamos el intervalo exacto desde que la pantalla se ilumina hasta
                    que la señal viaja de tus ojos al cerebro, y de ahí a tus dedos.
                </p>
                <div class="mt-6 flex flex-col gap-4">
                    <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
                        <Icon name="mdi:target" class="w-6 h-6 text-emerald-500 mt-1 shrink-0" />
                        <div>
                            <strong class="text-slate-900 dark:text-white block"
                                >Promedio de 5 Intentos</strong
                            >
                            <span class="text-sm"
                                >Eliminamos el factor "suerte" obligándote a ser consistente. Un
                                solo clic afortunado no te hará un Ciberatleta.</span
                            >
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
                        <Icon
                            name="mdi:shield-check"
                            class="w-6 h-6 text-amber-500 mt-1 shrink-0"
                        />
                        <div>
                            <strong class="text-slate-900 dark:text-white block"
                                >Sistema Anti-Trampas</strong
                            >
                            <span class="text-sm"
                                >Tiempos de espera aleatorios (1.5s - 4.5s) y detección de clics
                                anticipados para evitar predicciones.</span
                            >
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div
                class="bg-slate-50 dark:bg-slate-800/50 rounded-2xl p-6 border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700"
            >
                <div class="text-sm font-bold text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-widest mb-4">
                    La Ciencia
                </div>
                <div class="flex justify-between items-end mb-2">
                    <span class="text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400">Estímulo Visual</span>
                    <span class="font-mono text-xs text-slate-400">0 ms</span>
                </div>
                <div
                    class="h-2 w-full bg-slate-200 dark:bg-slate-700 rounded-full mb-4 overflow-hidden"
                >
                    <div class="h-full bg-indigo-500 w-full animate-pulse"></div>
                </div>

                <div class="flex justify-between items-end mb-2">
                    <span class="text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400">Procesamiento Cerebral</span>
                    <span class="font-mono text-xs text-slate-400">~180-200 ms</span>
                </div>
                <div
                    class="h-2 w-full bg-slate-200 dark:bg-slate-700 rounded-full mb-4 overflow-hidden"
                >
                    <div class="h-full bg-emerald-500 w-3/4"></div>
                </div>

                <div class="flex justify-between items-end mb-2">
                    <span class="text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400">Respuesta Motora</span>
                    <span class="font-mono text-xs text-slate-400">+20-40 ms</span>
                </div>
                <div class="h-2 w-full bg-slate-200 dark:bg-slate-700 rounded-full overflow-hidden">
                    <div class="h-full bg-amber-500 w-1/4"></div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-800 dark:text-white mb-6 flex items-center gap-2">
            <Icon name="mdi:trophy-variant" class="w-6 h-6 text-amber-500" />
            Tabla de Clasificación Mundial
        </h2>
        <div
            class="overflow-hidden rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700 shadow-sm bg-white dark:bg-slate-900"
        >
            <table class="w-full text-left border-collapse">
                <thead>
                    <tr
                        class="bg-slate-50 dark:bg-slate-800/50 text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400 text-xs uppercase tracking-wider"
                    >
                        <th class="p-4 font-bold border-b border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700"
                            >Tiempo</th
                        >
                        <th class="p-4 font-bold border-b border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700"
                            >Rango</th
                        >
                        <th
                            class="p-4 font-bold border-b border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700 hidden md:table-cell"
                            >Descripción</th
                        >
                    </tr>
                </thead>
                <tbody class="divide-y divide-slate-100 dark:divide-slate-800 text-sm">
                    <tr class="group hover:bg-cyan-50 dark:hover:bg-cyan-900/10 transition-colors">
                        <td class="p-4 font-mono font-bold text-cyan-600">&lt; 180 ms</td>
                        <td class="p-4">
                            <span
                                class="inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 px-3 py-1 rounded-full bg-cyan-100 dark:bg-cyan-900/30 text-cyan-700 dark:text-cyan-300 font-bold border border-cyan-200 dark:border-cyan-800"
                            >
                                <Icon name="mdi:lightning-bolt" class="w-3.5 h-3.5" /> Ciberatleta
                            </span>
                        </td>
                        <td class="p-4 text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400 hidden md:table-cell"
                            >Nivel sobrehumano propio de pros de eSports o pilotos de caza.</td
                        >
                    </tr>

                    <tr
                        class="group hover:bg-amber-50 dark:hover:bg-amber-900/10 transition-colors"
                    >
                        <td class="p-4 font-mono font-bold text-amber-600">180 - 230 ms</td>
                        <td class="p-4">
                            <span
                                class="inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 px-3 py-1 rounded-full bg-amber-100 dark:bg-amber-900/30 text-amber-700 dark:text-amber-300 font-bold border border-amber-200 dark:border-amber-800"
                            >
                                <Icon name="mdi:paw" class="w-3.5 h-3.5" /> Tigre
                            </span>
                        </td>
                        <td class="p-4 text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400 hidden md:table-cell"
                            >Reflejos afilados. Probablemente seas muy bueno en shooters.</td
                        >
                    </tr>

                    <tr
                        class="group hover:bg-emerald-50 dark:hover:bg-emerald-900/10 transition-colors"
                    >
                        <td class="p-4 font-mono font-bold text-emerald-600">230 - 280 ms</td>
                        <td class="p-4">
                            <span
                                class="inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 px-3 py-1 rounded-full bg-emerald-100 dark:bg-emerald-900/30 text-emerald-700 dark:text-emerald-300 font-bold border border-emerald-200 dark:border-emerald-800"
                            >
                                <Icon name="mdi:account" class="w-3.5 h-3.5" /> Humano
                            </span>
                        </td>
                        <td class="p-4 text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400 hidden md:table-cell"
                            >El promedio saludable. Estás despierto y funcionando correctamente.</td
                        >
                    </tr>

                    <tr
                        class="group hover:bg-slate-50 dark:hover:bg-slate-800/50 transition-colors"
                    >
                        <td class="p-4 font-mono font-bold text-slate-500">&gt; 350 ms</td>
                        <td class="p-4">
                            <span
                                class="inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 px-3 py-1 rounded-full bg-slate-100 dark:bg-slate-800 text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400 font-bold border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700"
                            >
                                <Icon name="mdi:coffee" class="w-3.5 h-3.5" /> Necesitas Café
                            </span>
                        </td>
                        <td class="p-4 text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400 hidden md:table-cell"
                            >Posible fatiga, sueño o hardware lento (input lag).</td
                        >
                    </tr>
                </tbody>
            </table>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-800 dark:text-white mb-6 flex items-center gap-2">
            <Icon name="mdi:tools" class="w-6 h-6 text-indigo-500" />
            ¿Por qué eres lento? Culpando al Hardware
        </h2>

        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
            <div
                class="bg-white dark:bg-slate-900 p-6 rounded-2xl shadow-sm border border-slate-100 dark:border-slate-800 hover:border-indigo-200 transition-colors"
            >
                <Icon name="mdi:monitor" class="w-10 h-10 text-cyan-500 mb-4" />
                <h3 class="font-bold text-slate-800 dark:text-white mb-2">Monitor (Hz)</h3>
                <p class="text-sm text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400 leading-relaxed">
                    Un monitor de <strong>60Hz</strong> tarda ~16ms en pintar un cuadro. Uno de <strong
                        >144Hz</strong
                    > tarda solo 7ms. Esa diferencia de 10ms cuenta en tu puntuación final.
                </p>
            </div>

            <div
                class="bg-white dark:bg-slate-900 p-6 rounded-2xl shadow-sm border border-slate-100 dark:border-slate-800 hover:border-indigo-200 transition-colors"
            >
                <Icon name="mdi:mouse-variant" class="w-10 h-10 text-purple-500 mb-4" />
                <h3 class="font-bold text-slate-800 dark:text-white mb-2">Ratón Inalámbrico</h3>
                <p class="text-sm text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400 leading-relaxed">
                    Los ratones bluetooth de oficina baratos tienen latencias altas. Para jugar (y
                    para este test), usa cable o tecnología wireless 2.4GHz de baja latencia.
                </p>
            </div>

            <div
                class="bg-white dark:bg-slate-900 p-6 rounded-2xl shadow-sm border border-slate-100 dark:border-slate-800 hover:border-indigo-200 transition-colors"
            >
                <Icon name="mdi:web" class="w-10 h-10 text-rose-500 mb-4" />
                <h3 class="font-bold text-slate-800 dark:text-white mb-2">Navegador</h3>
                <p class="text-sm text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400 leading-relaxed">
                    Las extensiones que bloquean anuncios o scripts pesados pueden causar
                    "stuttering". Prueba en modo incógnito si quieres tu récord real.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>
</div>
